### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

###

### Search skills
GET http://localhost:3000/api/skills/search?q=react+hooks+performance&k=5

###

### List all skills
GET http://localhost:3000/api/skills

###

### Get skill by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/skills/fg-css-specificity

###

### Scan project
POST http://localhost:3000/api/scan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": ".",
  "mode": "update"
}

###

### Detect anti-patterns
POST http://localhost:3000/api/skills/anti-patterns/detect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "const x = document.getElementById('myId'); x.style.color = 'red';"
}

###

### MCP tool call — search_skills
POST http://localhost:3000/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "search_skills",
    "arguments": {
      "query": "CSS BEM methodology specificity",
      "k": 3
    }
  }
}

###

### MCP tool call — get_enforcement_rules
POST http://localhost:3000/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "get_enforcement_rules",
    "arguments": {
      "domain": "Frontend Development Guidelines"
    }
  }
}

###

### MCP list tools
POST http://localhost:3000/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "method": "tools/list",
  "params": {}
}
